data.description: This charming bungalow features a huge front porch just waiting for your fall decorations! Enter the home and be greeted by a large living room and formal dining room with hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen and eat-in dining create plenty of room to entertain. Outdoor entertainment space continues with a covered patio, deck and oversized garage and driveway- there's room for everyone! Hang your hat in the mudroom off of the kitchen- laundry is on the main level! This home includes plenty of storage space and a huge secondary bedroom upstairs. This home has been waiting for you!
